"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1929127-adam-peaty-paris-olympics-team-gb\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Adam Peaty cried 'happy tears' despite coming second to Nicolo Martinenghi in the Men's 100m breaststroke at theParis Olympicson Sunday.Team GBstar Peaty was going for a third consecutive gold medal in his specialist event after fighting his way back to the pinnacle of the sport, but he fell 0.02 short as Italy clinched top spot.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871768069, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5858141376099518, \"rank\": 0.7069367608027143, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty's time of 59.05 seconds was more than two seconds shy of his personal best but still enough to take joint-second with American Nic Fink.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999969539418098, \"rank\": 2.5127583549346003e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nic Fink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany's Melvin Imoudu took the bronze, with Peaty's big rival, Qin Haiyang, finishing down in seventh.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9881574820150737, \"rank\": 0.010853368106030839, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gripping second 50m of the race saw the leading competitors strategically trying to time their last stroke perfectly.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Martinenghi managed to do just that, and in the end, that made the difference as Peaty missed out by the slimmest of margins.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a very long way back,\\\" Peaty, who has overcome mental health struggles, injuries and a split from the mother of his child, told theBBC.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gave my absolute all there.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the end goal, it's all about the process.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not matter what it says on the (timings) board - in my heart, I have already won.\\\"\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With tears beginning to flow, Peaty continued: \\\"I am not crying because I have come second.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am crying because it's taken so much to get here.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just incredibly hard to win it once and win it again and win it again.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have tried to find new ways to do it.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything I have done to this point has happened for a reason, and I am so happy I can race against the best in the world.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not crying because I lost, in my heart I have won.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These are happy tears.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said to myself I'd give my absolute best every day.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have and you can not be upset about that.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This event has changed so much.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a man now, I can not have that relentless pursuit every day without a sacrifice.\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very hard to compete with the younger ones.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My mind is on the relays now and trying to do my best for the team.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I know in my heart that I could not have done more.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are about who can perform at that moment, and I was just one or two per cent out.\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a very religious man and I asked God to just show my heart.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my heart, I could not have done more.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Six Olympic medals, right?\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not stick your nose up at that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2801, \"end\": 2814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.669350855686246e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2850, \"end\": 2